## Grading System

### Auto-Grading APIs
- [src/app/api/grade-assignment/route.ts](mdc:src/app/api/grade-assignment/route.ts) - Overall grading
- [src/app/api/grade-open-response/route.ts](mdc:src/app/api/grade-open-response/route.ts) - AI grading

### Grading Pattern
```typescript
// Multiple choice & numerical - instant
if (question.type === 'multiple-choice') {
  isCorrect = answer === question.correctAnswer
}

// Open response - AI powered
const gradeResponse = await fetch('/api/grade-open-response', {
  method: 'POST',
  body: JSON.stringify({
    question,
    studentAnswer
  })
})
```

## Storage Strategy

Assignments use localStorage with quota management in [src/utils/storage-utils.ts](mdc:src/utils/storage-utils.ts):
- Strip base64 images before storing
- Handle quota exceeded errors gracefully
- Automatic cleanup of old data